Cleanliness means that there is no dirt, no dust, no stains, no bad smells. 
The goals of cleanliness are health, beauty, absence of offensive odour and to avoid the spreading of dirt and contaminants to oneself and others.

With the help of cleanliness, we can keep our physical and mental health clean, which will make us feel good. XP 
Cleanliness gives rise to a good character by keeping body, mind, and soul clean and peaceful. 

Maintaining cleanliness is the essential part of healthy living because it is the cleanliness only which helps to improve our personality by keeping clean externally and internally.

